title: Star guardian icon
body: I took the quiz and when i retake it it tells me i already redeemed the icon. Its been a few days and i still haven't received said icon.

replies.body: It can take up to 72 hours for the icon to unlock on the account, sometimes longer.  The notification implies that you've redeemed it but it's still being processed.  Hang tight and the goodies will come!
I hope so - I am waiting since Day 1 ; w ; Still no Icon
It took me nearly a week to get mine after I took the quiz as soon as it came out...pretty sure it said it would take no more than 3 days..
